(1, 1, 'What is Google Cloud Platform? Why is it Important?', 'what-is-google-cloud-platform', 'In today\'s fast digital world, cloud computing has become a must-have rather than a trendy term. One of the big players in this field is Google Cloud Platform (GCP). It represents a collection of Google-offered cloud computing services that encompass a wide range of hosted services for computing, storage, AI and machine learning, big data, and more. Google built it on the same infrastructure as its end-user products like Google Search, Gmail, and YouTube.', 'GCP stands out for its robust data analytics and Machine Learning (ML) capabilities. With services like BigQuery and AutoML, businesses can innovate and scale seamlessly, staying competitive in the digital landscape. But what does all this mean for businesses, and why should you be interested in GCP? This article explains the benefits of GCP and why it\'s becoming increasingly important in the technology and business sectors.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/1.%20What%20is%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform_%20Why%20is%20it%20Important_.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629275', 2, 'Google Cloud Platform: What is it and Why is it important?', 'Discover why Google Cloud Platform is a major player in the cloud computing industry and how it helps to scale and optimize your business operations', 'Google Cloud Platform, what is Google Cloud platform', 2, '2024-02-22', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:48:15'),
(2, 1, 'The Essential Guide to Data Security Tools and Practices', 'data-security-tools-and-practices', 'Understanding data security is fundamental in today\'s digital landscape. With the internet being both an invaluable resource and a potential threat to the integrity of one\'s data, individuals and enterprises need to equip themselves with robust data security tools and practices.', 'This comprehensive guide will teach you the importance of data security, the various tools available, and the best practices that should become an integral part of your digital routine. Once you reach the end of this guide, you will have the knowledge to secure your digital footprint effectively.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/2.%20The%20Essential%20Guide%20to%20Data%20Security%20Tools%20and%20Practices.jpg?updatedAt=1712924633420', 3, 'A Complete Guide to Data Security Tools and Practices', 'This comprehensive guide to data security outlines the essential tools and best practices for safeguarding your data from cyber threats and breaches', 'data security, what is data security, data security tools, data security practices', 1, '2024-02-23', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:49:50'),
(3, 2, 'Top 5 Business Management Degree Programs in India', 'business-management-degree-programs', 'India has witnessed rapid economic growth in the past few decades, leading to a rise in demand for skilled business professionals. This has resulted in the emergence of various academic institutions offering specialized degree programs in business management.', 'These programs aim to equip young minds with the necessary knowledge and skills to succeed in the dynamic business world. Let\'s look at the top business management degree programs in India that are highly sought after by students and employers.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/3.%20Top%205%20Business%20Management%20Degree%20Programs%20in%20India.jpg?updatedAt=1712924632605', 2, 'Top 5 Business Management Degree Programs in India for 2024', '5 best business management degree programs in India for 2024. 1. Indian Institute of Management (IIM) • 2. Xavier School of Management (XLRI), and more.', '5 best business management degree,program management', 3, '2024-02-24', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:51:06'),
(4, 2, 'Top Digital Marketing Courses in 2024 for Beginners', 'digital-marketing-courses-for-beginners', 'Are you thinking about switching jobs or just want to get better at using technology? If so, digital marketing might be the right path for you. It\'s a growing field where you can learn a lot.', 'But there are so many online digital marketing courses that finding the right one can be time-consuming. This guide aims to provide a better understanding of which digital marketing course is suitable for a beginner in 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/4.%20Top%20Digital%20Marketing%20Courses%20in%202024%20for%20Beginners.jpg?updatedAt=1712924632301', 3, 'Best Digital Marketing Courses for Beginners in 2024', 'Want to start your career in digital marketing? Discover the best digital marketing courses for beginners in 2024 and learn the essential skills today', 'digital marketing courses, digital marketing, digital marketing course', 4, '2024-02-25', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:52:18'),
(5, 2, '5 Best Animation Courses in India for 2024', 'best-animation-courses', 'Animation is an incredibly dynamic and captivating field that draws in individuals with a flair for creativity and a knack for technology, all driven by the desire to breathe life into stories. With its expanding entertainment industry and globally recognized IT sector, India has become a leading hub for animation education, nurturing talent and fueling innovation in this exciting field.', 'With the onset of advanced technologies and digital platforms, the demand for skilled animators in India has accelerated, making it crucial to choose the right education path. Let\'s look at some of the best animation courses in India tailored for 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/5.%205%20Best%20Animation%20Courses%20in%20India%20for%202024.jpg?updatedAt=1712924633699', 4, '5 Best Animation Courses and Universities in India for 2024', 'Enroll in the best animation courses and universities in India for 2024. 1. National Institute of Design (NID) • 2. Whistling Woods International (WWI) & more.', 'animation courses and universities in India,animation', 5, '2024-02-26', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:53:56'),
(6, 3, 'Understanding Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, and Prevention', 'cataract-surgery-causes-symptoms-prevention', 'Cataracts affect millions yearly and are a leading cause of blindness worldwide. In the simplest terms, a cataract is a clouding of the eye\'s usually clear lens. For people who have been suffering from cataracts, their visibility becomes very similar to that of an average person trying to squint and watch through the fog or frostiness.', 'As a result, cataract victims might experience hurdles in reading or riding cars in the dark. This creates problems in day-to-day activities, so it is necessary to cure them. Ahead, we will help those looking to understand this condition, from its causes and symptoms to cataract-removal surgery.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/6.%20Understanding%20Cataract%20Surgery_%20Causes,%20Symptoms,%20and%20Prevention.jpg?updatedAt=1712924633556', 3, 'Cataract Surgery: Causes, Symptoms, and Prevention', 'While cataract surgery is generally safe and successful, it is essential to understand its causes, symptoms, and prevention to understand the subject matter.', 'Cataract Surgery', 2, '2024-02-27', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:55:17'),
(7, 4, 'The Benefits of Coworking Spaces for Digital Nomads', 'benefits-of-coworking-spaces-for-digital-nomads', 'The concept of coworking spaces has gained momentum over the past decade, dovetailing with the rise of digital nomadism and remote work culture.', 'Coworking spaces offer an office-like environment that fosters collaboration, productivity, and community among freelancers, entrepreneurs, and startups. In this blog, we will explore the manifold benefits of coworking spaces, particularly for digital nomads who seek flexibility without compromising professionalism.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/7.%20The%20Benefits%20of%20Coworking%20Spaces%20for%20Digital%20Nomads.jpg?updatedAt=1712924633483', 3, 'Coworking Space Benefits for Today’s Digital Nomads', 'Explore the benefits of coworking spaces for digital nomads, from fostering creativity and innovation to promoting work-life balance.', 'coworking spaces for digital nomads', 6, '2024-02-28', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:56:40'),
(8, 1, 'Cybersecurity Trends 2024: Protecting Your Digital Space', 'cybersecurity-trends', 'Cybersecurity has become an integral part of our digital existence. Each year, we witness new trends and strategies as cyberspace evolves. It\'s not just about protecting our data anymore; cybersecurity in 2024 is more complex and pervasive than we could have imagined even a decade ago. This year, we\'re seeing a focus on several key areas, from Generative AI to the rise of Quantum Computing.', 'You might wonder, what is cybersecurity? It involves protecting systems, networks, and software from digital attacks. Generally, these cyberattacks target sensitive information to access, alter, or destroy it, extort money from users, or disrupt normal business operations. Implementing effective cybersecurity measures is challenging because there are way more gadgets than people, and the attackers keep developing new tricks.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/8.%20Cybersecurity%20Trends%202024_%20Protecting%20Your%20Digital%20Space.jpg?updatedAt=1712924633411', 3, '7 Cybersecurity Trends For Your Digital Security in 2024', 'These cybersecurity trends for 2024 will help you know the importance of cybersecurity, its goals, and how it protects against threats in the digital world', 'Cybersecurity, cybersecurity courses, what is cybersecurity?, what are the three goals of cybersecurity?', 7, '2024-02-29', NULL, '2024-04-12 07:58:04'),
(10, 1, 'How to Choose the Right Security Camera System for Your Home', 'how-to-choose-the-right-home-security-system', 'Having a security camera system can make a significant difference in enhancing home safety and security.', 'Today, the sheer variety of security camera systems available can be overwhelming, but making the right choice hinges on several key factors. Homeowners considering investing in a security camera system must evaluate their needs, home environment, and available technology. Here\'s your ultimate guide on how to choose the perfect security camera system for your home.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/10.%20How%20to%20Choose%20the%20Right%20Security%20Camera%20System%20for%20Your%20Home.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629232', 2, 'How to Choose the Right Home Security Camera System', 'Know how to navigate through the essentials of choosing the perfect security camera system for your home. Before you buy, read this blog to know more.', 'home security camera system, security camera', 1, '2024-03-02', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:00:51'),
(11, 6, 'Top 10 Online Games You Need to Play in 2024', 'popular-online-games', 'The world of online gaming continues to surge in popularity every year. New titles are released each month, and the domain of what it means to play online games changes. Whether you are a seasoned player or a newcomer to the gaming community, staying in the loop with the best online games is essential.', 'In 2024, the online gaming scene has evolved and adapted to the gaming preferences of a global audience. These games offer immersive gameplay, stunning graphics, and competitive challenges, keeping players hooked. Thus, this article will give you a closer look at the top 10 online games that captivate players from every corner of the world.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/11%20Top%2010%20Online%20Games%20You%20Need%20to%20Play%20in%202024.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629265', 3, '10 Popular Online Games in the World 2024', 'Include these 10 online games in your 2024 gaming list. • 1. Roblox • 2. Minecraft • 3. Among Us • 4. Valorant • 5. Fortnite • 6. Apex Legends and more', 'online games, play online games, online games to play, best online games', 2, '2024-03-03', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:02:01'),
(12, 4, 'Top 6 Call Center Trends to Expect in 2024', 'call-center-trends', 'Today, customer service is at the heart of brand success, with the call center industry being a crucial pillar in this domain for decades, connecting businesses and their customers. However, keeping pace with customer experience expectations in an evolving landscape is a dynamic challenge.', 'Enterprises are continually seeking new ways to innovate their call center strategies. This blog post explores the emerging call center trends redefining customer service in 2024. From AI advancements to the remote workforce, these trends will surely bring exciting developments that promise to enhance customer satisfaction and streamline operations.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/12.%20Top%206%20Call%20Center%20Trends%20to%20Expect%20in%202024.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629408', 3, '6 Emerging Call Center Trends to Look Out for in 2024', 'Revolutionize your customer experience strategy. Explore Call Center Trends 2024 for insights into the latest industry developments and best practices', 'call center', 4, '2024-03-04', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:03:25'),
(13, 2, 'Impact of Technology on Employee Training & Develop', 'employee-training-and-development', 'The heartbeat of any successful company is its workforce, and for the heart to pump efficiently, it needs to be well-tuned and constantly developed. Employee training and development is not just a singular investment but an ongoing process that evolves as the business world changes.', 'While traditional methodologies have served their purpose, today\'s dynamic world demands a more tech-driven approach. Now is the time you acquaint yourself with the revolutionary power of technology in employee training and development and explore how innovative platforms are reshaping how we nurture talent in the modern workplace.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/13.%20Impact%20of%20Technology%20on%20Employee%20Training%20&%20Development.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629442', 2, 'Know How Technology Shapes Employee Training and Development', 'Explore the tangible benefits of using tech tools for employee training and development and learn how innovative tech solutions enhance workplace growth', 'employee training and development', 3, '2024-03-05', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:04:36'),
(14, 4, 'A Guide to Customer Data Analysis in Digital Marketing', 'customer-data-analysis', 'In the highly competitive digital market, the gap between what people watch or read online and how they behave is getting smaller quickly. Thus, the digital marketing landscape has metamorphosed from traditional market research to cutting-edge customer data analysis.', 'Businesses are shifting towards customer data analysis to tailor campaigns, predict needs, and create personalized experiences but often struggle to leverage this valuable information effectively. This guide provides them with a roadmap to utilize customer data, enhance marketing efforts, and adapt to the changing digital landscape.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/14.%20A%20Guide%20to%20Customer%20Data%20Analysis%20in%20Digital%20Marketing.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629674', 3, 'Customer Data Analysis Checklist for Digital Marketing', 'Revolutionize your digital marketing with customer data analysis. Learn to collect, analyze, and interpret data for optimized marketing performance', 'customer data analysis, digital marketing', 7, '2024-03-06', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:07:19'),
(15, 5, 'Effortless Luxury: Smart Solutions For Businesses & Homes', 'smart-solutions-for-businesses-and-homes', 'In the ever-evolving landscape of modern living, the definition of luxury constantly transforms. In 2024, luxury is no longer about opulence and extravagance but efficiency and innovation. Whether in the way of living or operating businesses, people constantly seek innovative solutions to streamline processes and enhance comfort.', 'Fortunately, recent technological advancements have made it possible to achieve efficiency and luxury simultaneously. Let\'s explore some innovative solutions to reshaping the landscape of business and residential spaces.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/15.%20Effortless%20Luxury_%20Smart%20Solutions%20For%20Businesses%20&%20Homes.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629402', 2, 'Effortlessly Luxurious | Solutions for Businesses & Homes', 'Explore innovative solutions that bring efficiency and luxury to businesses and homes, from smart automation and sustainable practices to AI integration & more.', 'Effortlessly Luxurious', 5, '2024-03-07', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:08:53'),
(16, 1, 'Popular Sales Software and Penetration Testing Services', 'most-popular-sales-software-penetration-testing-services', 'In this digital world, mastering the art of selling online and securing your software against cyber threats has never been more crucial. Sales professionals, software developers, and IT managers constantly seek innovative ways to boost performance and protect their digital environment.', 'Understanding the most popular sales software and the importance of penetration testing services is now a prerequisite for staying competitive and secure in today’s market.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/16.%20Popular%20Sales%20Software%20and%20Penetration%20Testing%20Services.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629469', 3, 'Most Popular Sales Software & Penetration Testing Services', 'Explore the top popular sales software and penetration testing services. 1. HubSpot Sales • Slack • Outreach • Metasploit • Nessus • Leadfeeder, and more.', 'top popular sales software', 6, '2024-03-08', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:10:05'),
(17, 3, 'Transforming Sectors: Healthcare, Real Estate, Manufacturing', 'industry-evolution-healthcare-real-estate-manufacturing', 'In today’s world, the rapid pace of innovation is revolutionizing industries. From healthcare that saves lives to real estate that connects community and manufacturing that underpins our consumer culture, each sector is experiencing transformations that propel them into a new era of efficiency and effectiveness.', 'Ahead, we will discuss the remarkable advancements transforming various industries. Specifically, we will explore the revolutionizing healthcare, real estate, and manufacturing developments.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/17.%20Transforming%20Sectors_%20Healthcare,%20Real%20Estate,%20Manufacturing.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629546', 3, 'Industry Evolution: Healthcare, Real Estate, Manufacturing', 'Explore the dynamic evolution of healthcare, real estate, and manufacturing sectors, uncovering key trends and innovations driving industry growth.', 'Industry Evolution: Healthcare, Real Estate, Manufacturing', 2, '2024-03-09', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:11:16'),
(18, 4, '5 Strategic Planning Tips for Business Growth in 2024', 'strategies-for-business-growth', 'In today\'s dynamic world of business and technology, facing challenges is like sailing through unknown seas. Businesses deal with digital changes, unpredictable markets, and constant innovation, which also bring opportunities and problems. This is when strategic planning and adaptability emerge to survive and thrive in such an evolving environment.', 'But what does it mean to be strategic when change is always happening? This blog will explore how successful businesses use technology and strategic thinking to turn challenges into opportunities, where it has become essential to thrive rather than just survive.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/18.%205%20Strategic%20Planning%20Tips%20for%20Business%20Growth%20in%202024.jpg?updatedAt=1712924629453', 3, '5 Key Strategies for Business Growth in 2024', 'Unlock success in 2024 with these 5 strategies for business growth. 1. Understand Your Market • 2. SMART Business Goals • 3. SWOT Analysis and more', 'MART Business Goals,5 Key Strategies for Business Growth', 4, '2024-03-10', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:12:52'),
(19, 4, 'Industrial Machines: Boosting Efficiency Across Sectors', 'industrial-machines-improve-work-efficiency ', 'In today’s ever-changing industrial world, business operations are dramatically transforming, especially within the manufacturing and industrial sectors. At the heart of this transformation lies industrial machines.', 'These indispensable tools have reshaped production processes, elevated efficiency levels, and increased productivity. In this article, we will understand how industrial machines drive business growth and bring work efficiency to modern industries while shaping their future.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/gku4adhog/fmr/New%20Articles/New%20Articles/19.%20Industrial%20Machines_%20Boosting%20Efficiency%20Across%20India.jpg?updatedAt=1712924632253', 2, 'Industrial Machines: Driving Efficiency Across Sectors', 'Industrial machines play a vital role in boosting efficiency across diverse industries. Learn how smart sensors and IoT increase industrial efficiency.', 'Industrial Machines,smart sensors and IoT increase industrial efficiency', 1, '2024-03-11', NULL, '2024-04-12 08:15:15'),
(20, 7, '$43/HR Office Cleaning Jobs With No Prior Experience', 'dollar-43-hr-office-cleaning-jobs-with-no-experience', 'For many, an \"office cleaning job\" might invoke images of mundane tasks and a never-ending sanitation cycle. Yet, when you look deeper, you will find that it is an industry with continuous growth, dynamic work environments, and many benefits that can transform your workspace and livelihood.', 'Whether you are at the beginning of your career, considering a change, or intrigued by the sanitation world, this blog aims to give you a deep understanding of the potential of office cleaning jobs and the career advancement that this essential job role can offer, keeping you engaged and informed throughout.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Office_cleaning_jobs_lDmaLuvkjJ.jpg?updatedAt=1713353172526', 2, '$43/HR Office Cleaning Jobs: No Experience Required', 'Get hired for high-paying office cleaning jobs at $43/hour without prior experience.  Start earning a competitive wage and build a prosperous future', 'office cleaning jobs, office cleaning, office cleaning services', 1, '2024-03-12', NULL, '2024-04-17 10:55:45'),
(21, 7, 'High-Paying Circuit Board Assembly Roles: $51/HR, Entry-Level & Equal Opportunity', 'dollar-51-hr-circuit-board-assembly-jobs-with-no-experience', 'As technology increasingly intertwines with our daily lives, the need for skilled labor in tech manufacturing is surging. If you\'re seeking a rewarding job that combines practical hands-on tasks with a technological knack and doesn\'t demand prior experience, circuit board assembly roles could be an ideal match for you.', 'Circuit board assemblers are crucial in manufacturing electronic devices that keep us connected. And the best part? There are positions offering an impressive $51 per hour salary, open to male and female candidates with no experience necessary.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Circuit_board_assembler_jobs_Bx0es26o6.jpg?updatedAt=1713353171448', 3, '$51/HR Circuit Board Assembly Jobs: No Experience Required', '$51/HR Circuit Board Assembly Jobs are available for entry-level males & females. Don’t miss the chance to get hired—your job opportunity is just a click away!', '$51/HR Circuit Board Assembly Jobs', 2, '2024-03-13', NULL, '2024-04-17 10:58:18'),
(22, 5, 'Two-Bedroom Apartments | From $350/Month | Prime Location', 'two-bedroom-apartments-at-prime-location', 'Are you looking for a luxurious apartment in a prime location that offers warmth, comfort, and convenience? We’ve got you covered. Two-bedroom apartments with ample amenities and convenience are now available for just $350/month in some of the most popular locations. \r\n', 'Prime location apartments, nestled in the heart of bustling city life, are sought for convenience, accessibility, and overall desirability. It\'s no wonder that luxurious two-bedroom apartments in prime locations are generating buzz among numerous renters.\r\n', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Two_bedroom_apartments_for_rent_N1hoKkTxn.jpg?updatedAt=1713353172896', 3, 'From $350/Month | Two-Bedroom Apartments | Prime Location', 'Luxurious two-bedroom apartments in a prime location starting at just $350/month! Ample amenities and convenient living await.', 'Luxurious two-bedroom apartments', 3, '2024-03-14', NULL, '2024-04-17 11:13:17'),
(23, 7, 'Hiring for a $51/HR Home Care Jobs With No Experience Required ', 'hiring-for-home-care-jobs-with-no-experience-needed', 'In a world of uncertainty and rapid change, job seekers often seek a career path that offers stability, fulfillment, and an attractive salary. The home care industry presents such an opportunity, allowing individuals to make a significant impact in the lives of others while securing their financial independence—even without prior experience.', 'Men and women alike are finding a rewarding future in the growing field of home care, where professionals provide support and companionship to those needing assistance with daily living.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Home_care_jobs_RokVEq7PSo.jpg?updatedAt=1713353169090', 2, 'Hiring for a  $51/HR Home Care Jobs With No Experience Needed', 'Get Home Care Jobs at $51/HR for males and females with no experience required at all. Join now, if you don’t want to miss out on this lucrative opportunity.', 'Home Care Jobs', 4, '2024-03-15', NULL, '2024-04-17 11:14:57'),
(24, 7, 'Get $51/HR WAREHOUSE PACKING JOBS WITH ZERO EXPERIENCE REQUIRED | BOTH MALE & FEMALE!', 'warehouse-packaging-jobs', 'In a world where job opportunities often demand extensive qualifications and experience, stumbling upon a lucrative prospect that requires neither can feel like stumbling upon a hidden treasure. Imagine earning $51 per hour without prior experience—seems too good to be true, right?', 'However, such opportunities do exist, and they\'re not as rare as one might think. Take warehouse packing jobs, for example, where both male and female individuals are welcomed with open arms and receive fair compensation.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/ThePromiseof51HRWarehousePackingJobsAPathwaytoOpportunityforAll_5MTs9ngir1.jpg?updatedAt=1713353110829', 2, '$51/Hr Warehouse Packaging Jobs For Both Female and Male', 'Warehouse packaging jobs are available for both males and females and pay $51/hr. The positions don’t require any prior experience & offer equal opportunities. ', 'Warehouse Packaging Jobs', 2, '2024-03-16', NULL, '2024-04-17 11:16:50'),
(25, 3, 'Medicare Tablets: An Essential Guide For Seniors', 'medicare-tablets-for-seniors', 'In today\'s digital age, technology has become indispensable, especially for seniors navigating their healthcare journey. With Medicare tablets, seniors can access many resources and services at their fingertips.', 'These devices offer convenience and empowerment, from checking coverage and benefits to scheduling appointments and paying bills. In this guide, we\'ll delve into the benefits of tablets for seniors and provide valuable insights on choosing the perfect device to suit their needs.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Medicare_Tablets_An_Essential_Guide_For_Seniors_GEKX78zJI.jpg?updatedAt=1713780872885', 3, 'Tablets With Medicare: An Essential Guide For Seniors', 'Medicare Tablets are a smart and easy way for seniors to access their healthcare information. Learn their benefits and choose the perfect one from our list.', 'Medicare Tablets benefits', 1, '2024-03-17', NULL, '2024-04-17 11:19:02'),
(27, 4, 'Cashback Credit Cards with No Credit Score Restrictions', 'cash-back-credit-cards-with-no-credit-score-restrictions', 'In a finance-driven world where every penny saved is a penny earned, cash-back credit cards have become an essential tool for millennials and young professionals who are keen to maximize their earnings and spend smarter.', 'Traditional credit cards are being sidestepped in favor of those offering cash-back rewards, especially those with substantial limits of £7,000 or more and accessibility without stringent credit score demands. We will explore such financial products ahead, focusing on four particularly popular options.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/CashbackCreditCardsWithoutAnyCreditScoreRestrictions_gAg1oT-A3.jpg?updatedAt=1713353110596', 2, 'Best Cashback Credit Cards with ₤ 7K Limit Or More', 'Cashback credit cards with ₤ 7K limit or more and with no credit score restrictions. 1. Chase Sapphire Preferred Card • 2. Petal 2 Visa Credit Card & more.', 'Best Cashback Credit Cards', 4, '2024-03-19', NULL, '2024-04-17 11:20:53'),
