(152, 3, 'Understanding Tardive Dyskinesia: Signs, Treatments & More', 'understanding-tardive-dyskinesia', 'Tardive dyskinesia (TD) is a neurological disorder that occurs as a side effect of long-term use of antipsychotic medications. These medications, while essential in managing psychiatric conditions like schizophrenia or bipolar disorder, can lead to involuntary movements in various parts of the body. This condition can be distressing and significantly impact a person’s quality of life. ', 'Here, we’ll explore the signs of tardive dyskinesia, potential treatments, and how to manage the condition effectively.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/152_H8olfxw59V.jpg?updatedAt=1729508067827', 3, 'Tardive Dyskinesia: Causes, Signs and Treatments', 'Learn how to identify the symptoms of tardive dyskinesia and understand its causes, signs, and latest treatment solutions for managing symptoms.', 'Tardive Dyskinesia Signs Treatments', 1, '2024-08-15', NULL, '2024-10-21 10:00:08'),
(153, 3, 'Multiple Sclerosis Treatment Options You Must Know', 'multiple-sclerosis-treatment', 'Multiple sclerosis (MS) is a chronic autoimmune disease that affects the central nervous system, causing damage to the brain, spinal cord, and optic nerves. It is estimated that over 2.5 million people around the world are affected by MS, with women being two to three times more likely to develop the disease than men.', 'While there is currently no cure for MS, there are various treatment options available that can help manage symptoms and slow down the progression of the disease. The most common treatment approaches for MS include medication, physical therapy, lifestyle changes, and alternative therapies. Here\'s a brief explanation of each treatment option you can implement today.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/153_q_U7F3adJn.jpg?updatedAt=1729508068254', 2, 'Understanding Multiple Sclerosis Treatment Options', 'Learn about treatment options for multiple sclerosis and how medications, therapies, and lifestyle changes can help manage MS symptoms.', 'Multiple Sclerosis Treatment', 2, '2024-08-16', NULL, '2024-10-21 10:02:14'),
(154, 3, 'A Guide to Leukemia: Signs, Causes, and Treatments', 'leukemia-guide', 'Leukemia is a word that can stir a lot of emotions and questions, but understanding it is the first step towards managing its impact. This blood cancer affects millions worldwide, yet many people still find it confusing or intimidating. ', 'In this guide, we\'ll break down leukemia into simple terms, discussing what it is, its signs, causes, and available treatments. This post will provide clarity and insight into this complex disease, whether personally or supporting a loved one.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/154_mzjagyXai.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654357', 2, 'Leukemia Guide: Understanding Signs, Causes and Treatments', 'Learn everything you must know about Leukemia, including its signs, causes, and treatment options. Gain insights to manage this challenging blood cancer.', 'Leukemia Signs Causes Treatment', 3, '2024-08-17', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:10:08'),
(155, 3, 'Everything You Need to Know About Bone Density Tests', 'all-about-bone-density-tests', 'Bone density tests might not be a topic you often consider, but they are crucial in maintaining your skeletal health, especially as you age. If you\'ve ever wondered why these tests are essential, how they work, or when you should consider getting one, you\'re in the right place. We’re covering everything you need to know about bone density tests in a conversational and informative way.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/155_KRT5JD3BC.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654410', 3, 'Bone Density Tests: Everything You Need to Know', 'Bone density tests help maintain bone health, identify early signs of osteoporosis, and more. Learn how they work and who should get tested today!', 'Bone Density Test', 4, '2024-08-18', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:12:29'),
(156, 5, 'Why Choose Private Jet Rentals for Your Next Trip?', 'why-to-choose-private-jet-rentals', 'Have you ever imagined traveling in ultimate luxury, free from the hassles of commercial air travel? Consider the world of private jet rentals, where luxury meets convenience. For discerning travelers seeking comfort, flexibility, and privacy, renting a private jet offers an unmatched experience. In this post, we’ll explore why private jet rentals are becoming increasingly popular and why they might be the perfect option for your next trip.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/156_2VC2ycfF4q.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654883', 3, 'Why are Private Jet Rentals a Smart Choice?', 'Find why private jet rentals are a smart choice for travelers. The benefits are endless, from luxury and privacy to flexible schedules and cost efficiency.', 'Private Jet Rentals', 5, '2024-08-19', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:14:59'),
(157, 3, 'What is Nash? | Signs, Causes, Treatments and More', 'nash-signs-causes-treatments', 'Nonalcoholic Steatohepatitis (NASH) is a liver condition that often flies under the radar but can have serious health implications if not addressed. As a more severe form of nonalcoholic fatty liver disease (NAFLD), NASH involves the accumulation of fat in the liver, leading to inflammation and liver damage. This condition can progress to cirrhosis, liver failure, or even liver cancer. ', 'Living with NASH can be challenging, but with the right information and proactive management, it\'s possible to mitigate its effects and maintain a healthy liver. So, it\'s essential to understand what NASH is, its causes, what early symptoms to look out for, and how it can be treated.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/157_kZvGRHYR50.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654747', 2, 'All About NASH: Signs, Causes, Treatments and More', 'NASH is a severe liver condition that can lead to cirrhosis and liver cancer.  Uncover its signs, causes, and treatments to mitigate this silent condition.', 'Nash signs Cause Treatment', 6, '2024-08-20', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:17:40'),
(158, 5, 'How to Find the Right Oil Change Specials For Seniors', 'tips-to-find-oil-change-specials-for-seniors', 'Keeping your car in top condition is crucial, especially as it ages alongside you. Regular oil changes are vital for vehicle maintenance, but costs can quickly increase with time. If you\'re retired or living on a fixed income, finding ways to save on oil changes becomes even more critical. Fortunately, there are several smart strategies to keep your vehicle running smoothly without breaking the bank.', 'Here, we explore practical tips to help seniors save on oil changes. Whether snagging a discount or avoiding unnecessary costs, these strategies make maintaining your car affordable and hassle-free.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/158_s29rUPIrQS.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654874', 2, 'Tips to Find the Right Oil Change Specials for Seniors', 'Find the best ways for seniors to reduce oil change expenses with coupons and special offers. Maintain your car affordably with our smart tips.', 'Oil Change Specials For Seniors', 7, '2024-08-21', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:19:47'),
(159, 5, 'Essential Tips for Choosing the Right Retirement Village', 'how-to-choose-a-retirement-village', 'Choosing a retirement village is a significant decision that requires careful consideration and planning. It’s not just about finding a place to live; it’s about finding a community that meets your lifestyle needs, health requirements, and personal preferences. With so many options available, the process can feel overwhelming. However, with the right approach, you can find a retirement village that offers a fulfilling and comfortable living experience.', 'Retirement should be a time of relaxation, enjoyment, and new experiences. A well-chosen retirement village can provide the perfect environment for this next chapter of your life. Here are some tips to help you make an informed decision.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/159_FffwzhYWWT.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654890', 3, 'How to Choose the Best Retirement Village', 'Get tips for selecting a retirement village that suits your lifestyle and health needs. From budgeting to location, learn how to choose the right one for you.', 'Retirement Village', 8, '2024-08-22', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:23:51'),
(160, 2, '5 Benefits of Registered Nursing Program Online', 'benefits-of-registered-nursing-program-online', 'The healthcare field is constantly evolving, and one of the most significant changes in recent years has been the rise of online education. Online registered nursing programs have become increasingly popular, offering flexibility and accessibility that traditional programs may lack. If you’re considering a career in nursing or looking to advance your current nursing education, here are 5 benefits of enrolling in a registered nursing program online.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/160_9DOML_o_D4.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654406', 3, 'Top 5 Benefits of Registered Nursing Program Online', 'Enhance your nursing career through online education. Understand how online RN programs offer accessibility and convenience for aspiring nurses.', 'Registered Nursing Program Online', 1, '2024-08-23', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:30:04'),
(161, 3, 'Parkinson’s Disease: Signs, Treatment & More', 'parkinsons-disease-signs-and-treatment', 'Most of us have heard of Parkinson’s disease, but what does it entail? This chronic and progressive neurological disorder affects movement, muscle control, and balance, and it usually creeps up gradually. Famous faces like Michael J. Fox and Muhammad Ali have brought visibility to the condition, yet many aspects of Parkinson’s remain misunderstood. Let’s break it down in a way that’s both informative and easy to understand.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/161_VJEuqWImff.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654658', 2, 'Understanding Parkinson’s Disease: Signs and Treatments', 'Learn about Parkinson’s disease, its symptoms, causes, and treatment options. Get insights into managing life effectively with Parkinson’s.', 'Parkinsons Disease Signs Treatment', 2, '2024-08-24', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:32:01'),
(162, 3, 'Colitis Diet: What to Eat and What to Avoid', 'colitis-diet', 'If you’ve been diagnosed with colitis, you’re probably aware that diet plays a huge role in managing your symptoms. Colitis—inflammation in the colon\'s lining can cause uncomfortable issues like cramping, bloating, and diarrhea. While food isn’t the root cause of colitis, it can aggravate or ease symptoms. So, knowing what to eat and avoid can make a difference in your daily life.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/162_MqUQL7j_Qj.jpg?updatedAt=1729594655085', 2, 'What Foods to Eat and Avoid When on a Colitis Diet?', 'A comprehensive guide to a colitis-friendly diet. Know what foods you can eat and avoid with our guide to plan your meals effectively.', 'Colitis Diet', 3, '2024-08-25', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:34:02'),
(163, 3, 'Must-Know Risks and Side Effects Of Coolsculpting', 'risks-and-side-effects-of-coolsculpting', 'Coolsculpting has emerged as a popular noninvasive procedure for eliminating stubborn fat cells without surgery. Marketed as a safer alternative to liposuction, this fat-freezing technique promises noticeable results with minimal downtime. In this blog, we will explain the pros and cons of Coolsculpting to help you make an informed decision. ', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/163_mVaOXM56vg.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562122', 3, 'Must-Know Risks and Side Effects Of Coolsculpting', 'Learn who should avoid Coolsculpting, a fat-freezing treatment. Make an informed decision based on the associated risks and side effects.', 'Coolscultping', 4, '2024-08-26', NULL, '2024-10-23 05:25:40'),
(164, 5, 'Surprising Benefits of Window Blinds You Need to Know', 'benefits-of-window-blinds', 'Window blinds are more than just a simple addition to your home decor. They offer many benefits that can transform your living space in ways you might not expect. Whether you\'re looking for privacy, energy efficiency, or a stylish touch, window blinds have something to offer everyone. In this blog post, we’ll explore the seven key benefits of window blinds and how they can enrich your living environment.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/164_h3QDAul8QH.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562407', 3, 'Discover the Benefits of Window Blinds for Your Home', 'Learn how window blinds improve privacy, save energy, and add style. Explore the top seven reasons to choose blinds for your windows today.', 'Window Blinds', 5, '2024-08-27', NULL, '2024-10-23 05:31:10'),
(165, 5, '7 Reasons Why Accident Lawyers Make Life Easier', 'benefits-of-hiring-accident-lawyers ', 'Navigating the aftermath of an accident can be overwhelming. The process is stressful and uncertain, from dealing with insurance companies to handling medical bills. This is where hiring an accident lawyer can make all the difference. Accident lawyers are skilled professionals who help injured parties receive the compensation they deserve. This blog post will explore the seven key benefits of hiring an accident lawyer, providing valuable insights and practical tips to guide you through these challenging times.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/165_27XRMrf82v.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562237', 2, '7 Reasons Why Accident Lawyers Make Life Easier ', 'Explore seven essential advantages of hiring accident lawyers and how they improve your legal experience following an accident.', 'Accident Lawyers ', 7, '2024-08-28', NULL, '2024-10-23 05:34:41'),
(166, 5, '7 Benefits of Hiring Workers Compensation Lawyers', 'benefits-of-hiring-workers-compensation-lawyers', 'Workers\' compensation laws exist to protect employees who suffer work-related injuries or illnesses. They ensure they receive medical treatment, wage replacement, and other benefits without proving the employer\'s fault. However, navigating the complexities of these laws can be challenging for both employees and employers. ', 'Workers\' compensation lawyers help injured workers navigate claims, protect their rights, and secure entitlement benefits. In this blog, we will explore the 7 advantages of hiring workers\' compensation lawyers today.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/166_wVZDjl6y7.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562504', 2, '7 Advantages of Hiring Workers Compensation Lawyers', 'Discover how hiring workers\' compensation lawyers can help maximize your benefits and navigate the claims process smoothly.', 'Workers Compensation Lawyers', 8, '2024-08-29', NULL, '2024-10-23 05:36:46'),
(167, 5, 'How to Choose the Best Personal Injury Lawyer for Your Case', 'how-to-choose-personal-injury-lawyer', 'Choosing the right personal injury lawyer can make all the difference in getting the compensation you deserve. Whether it’s a car accident, slip and fall, or medical malpractice case, having a skilled and trustworthy lawyer by your side can ease the stress of the legal process and maximize your chances of a successful outcome. Here are a few key things to consider when selecting the best personal injury lawyer for your case.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/167_2RbiEgLPrk.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562145', 3, 'How to Find the Right Personal Injury Lawyer for Your Case', 'Looking for a trustworthy personal injury lawyer? Explore essential qualities and tips to help you make the right decision for your legal needs.', 'Personal Injury Lawyer', 1, '2024-08-30', NULL, '2024-10-23 05:39:02'),
(168, 5, '5 Types of Insurance Plans Everyone Should Know', 'types-of-insurance-plans', 'Insurance is crucial to financial planning, offering a safety net when life takes unexpected turns. But with so many insurance plans, it’s easy to feel overwhelmed. Whether you’re preparing for your family’s future, your health, or protecting your assets, understanding the different types of insurance is critical. Here’s a quick guide to some of the most common insurance plans you should know about.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/168_hMEz2GIv2.jpg?updatedAt=1729677561701', 3, '5  Most Common Types of Insurance Plans Everyone Should Know', 'If you’re searching for various insurance plans, you’re at the right place. Read our guide to know the 5 types of insurance plans everyone must know.', 'Insurance Plans', 2, '2024-08-31', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:06:00'),
(169, 5, 'The Top Benefits of Assisted Living You Must Know', 'benefits-of-assisted-living', 'Assisted living has become famous for seniors who want to maintain their independence but need extra help with daily tasks. This type of senior living arrangement balances independent living and round-the-clock care in a comfortable and safe environment.', 'Assisted living has several benefits beyond just assistance, making it an attractive and perfect option for older adults. In this blog, we will explore these benefits in detail to help you understand why assisted living may be the best choice for your loved one.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/169_0dJ3vzEX8.jpg?updatedAt=1729677561905', 2, 'Top 5 Benefits of Assisted Living for Seniors You Must Know', 'Know the top 5 benefits of assisted living, from personalized care to maintenance-free living. Learn how these communities enhance seniors’ quality of life.', 'Assisted Living', 3, '2024-09-01', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:08:51'),
(170, 3, 'A Guide to Bladder Cancer: Symptoms and Effective Treatments', 'bladder-cancer-signs-and-treatments', 'Bladder cancer is a serious condition that affects thousands of people every year, but early detection can make a crucial difference in successful treatment. Unfortunately, many of the early warning signs of bladder cancer are often overlooked or mistaken for less severe conditions. In this blog, we’ll unveil signs of bladder cancer that you should never ignore and explore effective treatments to address them.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/170_CfHcnbTm-R.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562061', 3, 'Decoding Bladder Cancer: Signs and Effective Treatments', 'Discover the key signs of bladder cancer and learn effective strategies for early detection.', 'Bladder Cancer', 4, '2024-09-02', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:10:59'),
(171, 5, 'Vanguard Investments: 4 Things to Always Keep in Mind ', 'vanguard-investments-things-to-remember', 'Are you thinking about dipping your toes into the world of Vanguard investing? You\'re not alone! With its reputation for offering some of the best mutual funds and ETFs, especially for retirees, Vanguard has become a go-to for many investors. But with so many options, how do you decide which fund is right for you? Today, we\'ll explore four crucial aspects to consider when choosing a Vanguard fund, ensuring that your investment aligns with your financial goals.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/171_sVF4vFGMZv.jpg?updatedAt=1729677561697', 3, '4 Things to Always Remember About Vanguard Investments', 'Before trying your luck at Vanguard Investments, it’s wise to keep a few things in mind. Here are the top 4 essential things every investor should always know.', 'Vanguard Investment', 5, '2024-09-03', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:13:04'),
(172, 5, '4 Mistakes to Avoid When Purchasing Pet Insurance', 'pet-insurance-purchase-mistakes', 'Pet insurance is becoming increasingly popular as pet owners realize the benefits of having financial coverage for their furry companions. However, purchasing pet insurance can be tricky, especially if you\'re new to it. Mistakes made during the process might leave you with inadequate coverage or unexpected expenses. Understanding what to avoid is crucial in making wise decisions that will benefit you and your pet in the long run.', 'Here are four common mistakes to avoid when buying pet insurance. By avoiding these pitfalls, you\'ll ensure that you choose the right plan for your pet\'s needs while optimizing your expenses.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/172_cfhs8ndb44.jpg?updatedAt=1729677562229', 2, '4 Common Mistakes to Avoid When Buying Pet Insurance', 'Ready to buy pet insurance? Before you do, read about these 4 frequent errors pet owners make—and how you can dodge them for optimal coverage.', 'Pet Insurance', 6, '2024-09-04', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:14:58'),
(173, 3, 'Huntington’s Disease: The 6 Signs You Shouldn’t Ignore', 'symptoms-of-huntingtons-disease', 'Huntington’s disease is a genetic disorder that gradually affects the brain, leading to physical, cognitive, and emotional changes. Often, it goes unnoticed until symptoms become pronounced, making early recognition crucial for management and support. Understanding those who may not be familiar with the signs can make all the difference in seeking timely care and improving quality of life.', 'Here are the 6 most common signs of Huntington’s disease. This guide will help you identify potential symptoms early on, whether you\'re concerned about yourself or a loved one.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/173_lIHD8QJ2yM.jpg?updatedAt=1729677565487', 2, '6 Warning Signs of Huntington’s Disease You Must Not Ignore', 'Huntington\'s disease can be challenging, but recognizing the signs early can aid management. Here are 6 symptoms you need to look out for.', 'Huntington\'s Disease', 7, '2024-09-05', NULL, '2024-10-23 06:17:44'),
(174, 5, '7 Key Factors for Planning Which AI Stocks to Buy', 'factors-to-consider-before-investing-in-ai-stocks', 'In an era where technological advancements dictate the pace of business innovation, artificial intelligence (AI) stands as a beacon of transformation. It reshapes industries, accelerates processes, and opens new avenues for growth. For investors, AI presents a dynamic landscape filled with opportunities and challenges. In this blog, we will explore the key considerations when investing in AI, equipping you with insights to make informed decisions and capitalize on AI\'s potential to drive success.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/174_wuHS1iHBj.jpg?updatedAt=1729769429090', 3, '7 Key Factors for Planning Which AI Stocks to Buy', 'Explore 7 vital factors when investing in AI. Learn about industry applications, ethical considerations, and promising opportunities.', 'AI Stocks To Buy', 8, '2024-09-06', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:10:55'),
(175, 5, 'Top 5 Factors That Affect Your Mortgage Interest Rates', 'factors-affecting-mortgage-interest-rates', 'Buying a home is one of the most significant financial decisions you\'ll make, and understanding the factors that influence your mortgage interest rates can help you make informed choices. Whether you\'re a first-time buyer or looking to refinance, knowing what affects your rate can save you thousands over the life of your loan. ', 'Here, we\'ll explore the top 5 factors impacting your mortgage interest rates, giving you the insights you need to secure the best deal possible.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/175_F6zQCYIY1n.jpg?updatedAt=1729769429564', 3, 'The Top 5 Factors Affecting Mortgage Interest Rates', 'Learn how credit scores, economic conditions, and more affect your mortgage interest rate. Get the knowledge you need to secure the best possible deal.', 'Mortgage Interest Rates', 1, '2024-09-07', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:13:00'),
(176, 2, 'Everything You Need to Know About High School Diploma Online', 'all-about-high-school-diploma-online', 'With the rise of the internet and its vast availability, online school programs have gained significant popularity. Students now have the option to pursue their high school diplomas from the comfort of their own homes. But before diving in, it\'s essential to understand the ins and outs of online high school diplomas, including the difference between free and paid programs and how they function.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/176_c0-R-ox9u.jpg?updatedAt=1729769427934', 3, 'High School Diploma Online: Everything You Need to Know', 'Know the ins and outs of online high school diplomas, including types, accreditation, and their acceptance in higher education and employment.', 'High School Diploma Online', 2, '2024-09-08', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:16:16'),
(177, 3, 'Causes and Effective Low Platelets Treatment Options', 'causes-and-treatment-for-low-platelets', 'Low platelets, medically known as thrombocytopenia, can cause concern. Whether it\'s a temporary or chronic issue, understanding what causes low platelet counts and how they can be treated is crucial. If you\'re experiencing symptoms related to this condition or simply want to know more, this blog will explore some common causes of low platelets and discuss effective treatments to help manage and improve this condition.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/177_pKq6T5mmr.jpg?updatedAt=1729769428827', 2, 'Causes and Effective Low Platelets Treatment Explained ', 'Explore the causes and treatment options for low platelet counts. Gain insights on effectively managing thrombocytopenia for better health outcomes.', 'Low Platelets Treatment', 3, '2024-09-09', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:18:04'),
(178, 3, 'A Detailed Guide to Myelofibrosis Treatments and Causes', 'myelofibrosis-treatments-and-causes', 'When it comes to navigating the complex world of chronic illnesses, Myelofibrosis stands out as a unique condition that affects the body\'s ability to produce blood cells. This rare blood cancer can transform a patient\'s life, bringing with it a range of symptoms and complications. ', 'Understanding the causes and treatments of Myelofibrosis is crucial for those affected, their families, and their caregivers. In this blog, we\'ll understand what causes this condition and explore the treatments available to manage it.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/178_gjYOsFtDf8.jpg?updatedAt=1729769429240', 3, 'Your Guide to Myelofibrosis Treatments and Causes', 'Myelofibrosis is a rare blood cancer that can heavily affect your routine. Understand its causes and treatment options to navigate this condition effectively.', 'Myelofibrosis Treatments', 4, '2024-09-10', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:20:09'),
(179, 3, 'Best Vitamins for Menopause Management', 'best-vitamins-for-menopause', 'Menopause marks a significant transition in every woman\'s life, bringing with it a range of symptoms that can vary significantly in their intensity and impact. While some sail through with minimal disruptions, others face hot flashes, insomnia, mood swings, and more. This natural phase signifies the end of a woman\'s menstrual cycle and is often accompanied by a decrease in estrogen levels. Understanding how to manage menopause effectively can significantly improve the quality of life during this time.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/179_z2UDZYJny.jpg?updatedAt=1729769428859', 3, 'Best Vitamins for Menopause Management ', 'Explore the best vitamins for menopause to ease symptoms and support overall well-being during this transformative phase.', 'Best Vitamins For Menopause', 5, '2024-09-11', NULL, '2024-10-24 05:22:04'),
(180, 5, 'Black Friday Laptop Sales You Cannot Miss in 2024', 'black-friday-laptop-sales', 'Black Friday is the perfect time to snag a great deal on tech, especially laptops. Whether you\'re a student, a professional, or simply need an upgrade, the 2024 Black Friday sales promise incredible discounts on laptops from top brands. This year\'s deals are set to be hotter than ever, with significant savings that make it easy to invest in new technology without breaking the bank.', 'Here, we explore the most exciting laptop deals this Black Friday. We\'ll guide you through the best retailers to watch and highlight some standout offers you should take advantage of.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/180_f7JYIkKta.jpg?updatedAt=1731409276201', 2, 'The Best Black Friday Laptop Deals of 2024', 'Find the top Black Friday 2024 laptop deals. Dive into the sale rush and steal the best deals from major brands like Apple, HP, and Lenovo.', 'Black Friday Laptop Sales', 6, '2024-09-12', NULL, '2024-11-12 08:16:20'),
