(182, 5, 'Shop the Best Black Friday Jewelry Sales from Top Brands', 'best-black-friday-jewelry-sales', 'Black Friday is synonymous with unbeatable deals, and for jewelry shoppers, it\'s a golden opportunity to snag some dazzling pieces at a fraction of their usual price. If you want to splurge on some jewelry, you must know which brands offer the best Black Friday jewelry sales to save time and money. ', 'In this blog, we\'ll explore 5 brands known for their exceptional Black Friday Jewelry Sales, giving you a head start on the upcoming shopping extravaganza.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/182_JIR9T2TD8.jpg?updatedAt=1731409289297', 3, 'Shop the Best Black Friday Jewelry Sales from Top Brands', 'Get the best Black Friday jewelry deals from the industry\'s top brands. Find stunning pieces at jaw-dropping discounts!', 'Black Friday Jewelry Sales', 8, '2024-09-14', NULL, '2024-11-12 08:21:40'),
(183, 5, 'Top Black Friday Smartphone Deals That Are Hard to Miss', 'best-black-friday-smartphone-deals', 'The biggest shopping season is just around the corner, and it\'s time to gear up for some incredible smartphone savings. Black Friday is renowned for offering unbeatable deals, making it the perfect opportunity to upgrade your device without breaking the bank. In this blog, we will walk you through the top brands and retailers participating in this year\'s Black Friday sale and highlight the best offers.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/183_Ode_7zu63.jpg?updatedAt=1731409290707', 3, 'Shop the Best Black Friday Smartphone Deals', 'Upgrade your smartphone with top Black Friday deals at record-low prices.', 'Black Friday Smartphone Deals', 1, '2024-09-15', NULL, '2024-11-12 08:23:44'),
(184, 5, 'Black Friday Home Appliance Sales 2024', 'black-friday-home-appliance-sales', 'Black Friday is just around the corner, and if you\'re in the market for home appliances, you\'re in luck. This annual shopping event is the perfect opportunity to snag some of the best deals on everything from refrigerators to vacuum cleaners. ', 'In 2024, retailers are stepping up their game, offering jaw-dropping discounts that make upgrading your home easier. Whether you\'re looking for cutting-edge technology or simply want to replace an old appliance, this year\'s Black Friday sales will have something for everyone.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/184_0qQoQLFolr.jpg?updatedAt=1731409303453', 2, 'Save Big on Black Friday Home Appliance Sales 2024', 'Discover the hottest Black Friday 2024 home appliance deals from Best Buy, Lowe’s, and more. Save big on fridges, washers, and more.', 'Black Friday Home Appliance Sales', 2, '2024-09-16', NULL, '2024-11-12 08:29:33'),
(185, 5, 'Black Friday Furniture Sales - Save Big This Season', 'black-friday-furniture-sales', 'The holiday season is fast approaching, bringing the biggest shopping event of the year—Black Friday. If you\'re looking to refresh your living space, this is the perfect chance to grab amazing deals on furniture. Whether you need a modern couch, a luxurious dining set, or sleek office furniture, Black Friday offers discounts that make upgrading your home easier than ever. In this blog, we’ll highlight top retailers and brands, share their unique features, and give you a sneak peek at this year\'s anticipated discounts.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/185_vl3x_Wto9.jpg?updatedAt=1731409317991', 2, 'Black Friday Furniture Sales - Save Big This Season ', 'Discover Black Friday furniture sales with exclusive discounts on premium items and refresh your space with unbeatable offers and savings.', 'Black Friday Furniture Sales', 3, '2024-09-17', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:35:54'),
(186, 5, 'Sailing into Savings with Top Black Friday Cruise Deals 2024', 'black-friday-cruise-deals', 'The holiday season isn’t just about gifts, family gatherings, or feasting—it\'s also one of the best times to snag incredible cruise deals. Black Friday offers have swept across the cruise industry this year, allowing travelers to explore the world at extremely low prices.', 'This blog dives into some of the most enticing Black Friday cruise deals available for 2024. We’ll explore top offerings from famous cruise lines, helping you find the perfect trip for your next getaway. Read on to find the Black Friday Cruise Deals on the high seas.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/186_0IfzExXLX.jpg?updatedAt=1731409292404', 3, 'Sailing into Savings: Black Friday Cruise Deals 2024', 'Set sail on an unforgettable journey with these top Black Friday cruise deals for 2024. Save big on fares, earn onboard credits and experience luxury.', 'Black Friday Cruise Deals', 4, '2024-09-18', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:38:03'),
(187, 5, 'Top Cyber Monday Gift Cards for 2024 You Can\'t Miss', 'cyber-monday-gift-cards', 'Cyber Monday 2024 is just around the corner, and for savvy shoppers, it’s one of the best times of the year to buy gift cards. Not only do gift cards make great holiday gifts, but they’re also a clever way to save on future purchases. Many top U.S. e-commerce platforms are expected to offer special Cyber Monday deals on gift cards, whether in the form of discounts, bonus credits, or exclusive promotions. Here’s a rundown of where to find the best gift card deals on Cyber Monday this year.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/187_OjYvTlBvF.jpg?updatedAt=1731409295788', 3, 'Top Cyber Monday Gift Cards for 2024 You Shouldn\'t Ignore', 'Maximize your savings with Cyber Monday gift cards for 2024 from leading online stores. 1. Amazon • 2. Walmart • 3. Target • 4. Best Buy • 5. Costco', 'Cyber Monday Gift Cards', 5, '2024-09-19', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:40:09'),
