(189, 5, 'Top Black Friday & Cyber Monday Streaming Discounts 2024', 'black-friday-and-cyber-monday-streaming-discounts', 'With Black Friday and Cyber Monday just around the corner, there’s no better time to snag incredible deals on streaming services. Often overlooked, these deals can significantly reduce your monthly expenses while giving you access to various captivating shows and movies. ', 'This year, the streaming landscape has been more competitive than ever, with platforms vying for your attention through irresistible offers. In this post, we’ll explore some of the best streaming deals you can anticipate in 2024, ensuring you don’t miss out on anything exciting.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/189_ReaYHlg-0.jpg?updatedAt=1731409296265', 3, 'Black Friday & Cyber Monday Streaming Discounts of 2024', 'Don\'t miss out on the best Black Friday and Cyber Monday streaming deals of 2024! Find incredible discounts from Amazon Prime, Apple TV+, and more.', 'Cyber Monday Streaming Discounts', 7, '2024-09-21', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:44:31'),
(190, 5, 'Top Cyber Monday Electronics and Gadgets Products ', 'cyber-monday-electronics-and-gadgets-products', 'Every year, Cyber Monday arrives like a beacon of hope for tech enthusiasts and savvy shoppers alike. It\'s the day when prices on coveted gadgets and electronics drop to tantalizing lows, offering an irresistible opportunity to upgrade your tech arsenal. ', 'This year, prepare to immerse yourself in a sea of unbeatable deals that promise to deliver both value and cutting-edge technology. From smart televisions to sleek laptops and powerful smartphones, we\'ve curated a list of top-rated products you won\'t want to miss out on. ', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/190_n0GyB4pllU.jpg?updatedAt=1731409334075', 3, 'Best Cyber Monday Electronics and Gadgets Products ', 'Explore the top Cyber Monday deals on electronics and gadgets and snag incredible discounts on the best-rated TVs, laptops, and smartphones.', 'Cyber Monday Electronics and Gadgets Products', 8, '2024-09-22', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:49:24'),
(191, 5, 'Top Sites for Unbeatable Cyber Monday Smartphone Deals 2024', 'cyber-monday-smartphone-deals', 'In the fast-paced world of technology, staying up-to-date with the latest smartphones can be costly. Fortunately, Cyber Monday offers the perfect opportunity to snag incredible deals on top-notch devices. ', 'This year, several retail giants are pulling out all the stops to provide unbeatable discounts on smartphones and accessories. Covering Apple, Android, Google, Motorola, and more, these deals are too good to ignore. Let\'s explore the top sites where you can find the best Cyber Monday smartphone deals in 2024.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/191_n8gfMUAUj.jpg?updatedAt=1731409329454', 2, 'Top Sites for the Best Cyber Monday Smartphone Deals 2024', 'Discover unbeatable smartphone deals this Cyber Monday 2024! Find discounts on the latest devices from Best Buy, Amazon, AT&T, and T-Mobile.', 'Cyber Monday Smartphone Deals', 1, '2024-09-23', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:51:27'),
(192, 5, 'Cyber Monday Laptop Sales 2024: Save Big on Top Brands', 'cyber-monday-laptop-sales', 'Cyber Monday 2024 promises to be an extraordinary occasion for anyone seeking a new laptop. This event caters to a broad audience, including students aiming for academic excellence, gamers looking for high-performance machines, and professionals seeking reliable devices for work. In this blog, we’ve anticipated substantial discounts on various laptop brands and models, such as Apple, Dell, HP, Lenovo, and more.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/192_eyhpDBOPj.jpg?updatedAt=1731409340677', 2, 'Cyber Monday Laptop Sales 2024: Huge Savings Ahead', 'Get ready for the best Cyber Monday laptop sales in 2024! Discover top discounts on Apple, Dell, HP, Lenovo, and more, with deals perfect for every budget.', 'Cyber Monday Laptop Sales', 2, '2024-09-24', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:52:59'),
(193, 5, 'Hacks to Maximize Black Friday Deals & Offers 2024', 'black-friday-deals-and-offers', 'With the biggest shopping event of the year just around the corner, it\'s time to prepare for Black Friday 2024. This annual extravaganza offers shoppers the chance to score incredible deals on everything from electronics to clothing. But with so many offers available, how can you make sure you\'re getting the best bang for your buck? This guide will walk you through practical hacks to maximize your savings and make the most of this shopping season.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/193_kje_PsCk5.jpg?updatedAt=1731409340918', 3, 'Hacks to Maximize Black Friday Deals & Offers 2024', 'Get ahead of the Black Friday 2024 deals with essential hacks and expert tips to score amazing offers and achieve your shopping goals.', 'Black Friday Deals & Offers 2024', 3, '2024-09-25', NULL, '2024-11-12 09:55:53'),
