(40, 1, 'Smart Tech Solutions: Events, CMMS, and Fleet Management', 'tech-solutions-to-drive-business-efficiency', 'In the fast-paced world of business operations, efficiency is crucial to achieving success and staying competitive. Embracing smart technological solutions tailored for specific areas such as events management, Computerized Maintenance Management Systems (CMMS), and fleet management can make all the difference.', 'Fortunately, modern tech solutions offer a range of solutions that significantly enhance operational effectiveness, streamline processes, and optimize resource utilization across various sections. Let\'s explore how modern technology solutions can drive business efficiency and unlock new opportunities for growth and innovation.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Smart_Tech_Solutions__TYi7pNs0H.jpg?updatedAt=1713357932909', 2, 'Smart Solutions for Events, CMMS, and Fleet Management', 'Want to drive efficiency in your business? Learn how various tech solutions for events, CMMS, and fleet management can improve your work efficiency.', NULL, 1, '2024-04-01', NULL, '2024-04-17 12:15:48'),
(41, 3, 'Revolutionizing Healthcare: From AI Courses to Patient Engagement Software', 'patient-engagement-software', 'Today, when the world is running at a fast pace, and technology is evolving at an unprecedented rate, the healthcare industry is not lagging behind. These artificial intelligence (AI) courses empower medical professionals, and patient engagement software enhances the healthcare experience. Revolutionary advancements are shaping the future of healthcare delivery.', 'Let us see how these innovations are transforming the landscape of healthcare, bringing us closer to more personalized, efficient, and patient-centric care.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Revolutionizing_Healthcare_U0N-tbsHlp.jpg?updatedAt=1713357931792', 2, 'Innovating Healthcare: From AI Courses To Patient Engagement', 'The intersection of AI and patient engagement software in revolutionizing healthcare. These advancements drive efficiency, engagement, and better outcomes.', NULL, 1, '2024-04-02', NULL, '2024-04-17 12:16:59'),
(42, 5, 'Modern Solutions for Real Estate Management & Roofing', 'advanced-solutions-for-real-estate-management-and-roofing', 'The world of real estate management and roofing is undergoing a seismic shift, thanks to the advent of advanced technologies and solutions. Once riddled with inefficiencies and manual labor, property operations are now being transformed into models of efficiency and effectiveness.', 'This transition is enhancing how real estate managers, roofing contractors, and property owners operate and revolutionizing the entire industry.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Real_Estate_Management_xvu1GMXkEh.jpg?updatedAt=1713357933179', 3, 'Advanced Solutions for Real Estate Management & Roofing', 'Get modern solutions for real estate management and roofing. 1. Redefining Property Operations • 2. Elevating Maintenance & Sustainability, and more.', NULL, 4, '2024-04-03', NULL, '2024-04-17 12:18:08'),
(43, 4, 'Driving Business Growth with Automation: Marketing, Lead Management & Web Ads', 'business-growth-marketing-automation-lead-management-website-advertising', 'In the modern era, businesses continuously seek innovative ways to scale and augment their market presence. Growth is about more than mere survival; it\'s about thriving in a competitive landscape.', 'From marketing automation to lead management and website advertising, the key lies in integrating technology with strategy to achieve success. Ahead, we will discuss how you can drive growth for your business.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Empowering_Business_Growth_8oT85cBZg-.jpg?updatedAt=1713357931180', 3, 'Business Growth with Marketing, Leads & Web Ads Automation', 'Learn how to drive business growth through marketing automation, lead management, and website advertising. • Transforming Engagement Strategies and more.', NULL, 2, '2024-04-04', NULL, '2024-04-17 12:21:20'),
(44, 2, 'Thriving Amidst Contemporary Trials: Cyber Challenges, Anxiety Problems, and Industrial Advancements', 'navigating-the-new-normal', 'In today\'s fast-paced world, we find ourselves grappling with many modern challenges. We always think about safeguarding our digital footprints and managing our mental well-being. Also, we cannot overlook revolutionizing our industrial processes as the landscape of our lives is constantly evolving.', 'Let us look into three significant realms—cybersecurity testing, anxiety treatment, and industrial automation—and explore how we see through these contemporary trials with resilience and innovation.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Navigating_Modern_Challenges_mb32a77Sxk.jpg?updatedAt=1713357933369', 2, 'Contemporary Issues: Cybersecurity, Anxiety, Automation', 'The dynamic trio of cybersecurity, anxiety treatment, and industrial automation. Discover how to tackle modern challenges with resilience and innovation.', NULL, 2, '2024-04-05', NULL, '2024-04-17 12:23:12'),
(45, 5, 'Explore the Role & Significance of Attorneys in Society', 'role-and-significance-of-attorneys-in-society', 'Navigating the complexities of the law requires expert knowledge and skills that most laypeople do not possess. This is where attorneys come into play. As advocates and advisors, attorneys are critical to the justice system.', 'Ahead, we aim to shed light on the multifaceted role of an attorney and the importance of their presence in various aspects of life, whether you’re an individual in need of legal advice, a small business owner, or a budding law student.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Explore_the_Role_&_Significance_of_Attorneys_BYouYOvWL.jpg?updatedAt=1713438186421', 2, 'Understanding the Attorney\'s Roles & Importance in Society', 'Explore understanding the attorney’s roles and importance in society. 1. Functions & Objectives of an Attorney • 2. Qualifications & Experience & more.', 'attorney’s roles and importance in society', 2, '2024-04-06', NULL, '2024-04-18 07:17:07'),
(46, 5, 'Here’s How Walk-In Tubs Help Seniors Stay Safe at Home', 'walk-in-tubs-for-seniors', 'Simple tasks like bathing can become challenging as we age, and safety becomes a top priority. Fortunately, walk-in tubs have emerged as an innovative and practical solution, offering numerous benefits for seniors seeking a safe and comfortable bathing experience. ', 'These specially designed bathtubs are not just a luxury but an essential investment for seniors aiming for a blend of safety, comfort, and independence in their golden years. Here’s a closer look at the top 10 benefits of walk-in tubs for seniors that empower them to maintain self-reliance.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/Walk_In_Tubs_Help_Seniors_Stay_Safe_at_Home_Gd0OYBYto_.jpg?updatedAt=1713438187052', 3, 'Top 10 Benefits of Walk-In Tubs for Seniors', 'Discover the top benefits of walk-in tubs for seniors, including safety, hygiene, and more. Learn how they offer a healthier and more independent lifestyle.', 'Walk-In Tubs for Seniors', 3, '2024-04-07', NULL, '2024-04-18 07:18:48');
