(57, 4, 'The Dynamics of Steel Supply: Navigating the Industry\'s Complexities', 'steel-supply-dynamics', 'Steel is the cornerstone of contemporary industry and infrastructure, providing the framework for several vital products such as cars, skyscrapers, bridges, and many other items.', 'Its predominance is, however, the result of a dynamic and intricate supply network. Comprehending the subtleties of steel supply is imperative for both industry and customer since it influences many aspects, such as construction expenses and manufacturing schedules. We\'ll examine the subtleties of the steel supply chain and the major variables influencing its dynamics in this blog.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/57_31OdHHmWzg.jpg?updatedAt=1713438387353', 2, 'Steel Supply Chain: From Sourcing to Sustainability', 'Explore the intricate web of global demand, manufacturing capacities, and trade policies shaping the dynamics of steel supply in today\'s interconnected world.', 'Steel Supply Chain', 3, '2024-04-18', NULL, '2024-04-18 08:05:46'),
(58, 4, 'The World of Food Packing Jobs: Opportunities and Pathways', 'food-packing-jobs', 'Today, the food industry is just as important as any other, and the lifestyle that people live, the food industry stands as a cornerstone of society. In this dynamic landscape, food packing is one sector that often goes unnoticed yet plays a crucial role. From ensuring freshness to enhancing shelf appeal, packing professionals are the actual heroes behind the scenes. Have a glance at these food packing jobs, exploring its booming industry, diverse career paths, and key skills for success.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/58_YIl4Y9q2n5.jpg?updatedAt=1713438399894', 3, 'The World of Food Packing: Career Paths & Opportunities', 'Learn about how the food packing careers work. Learn about different career avenues and essential skills you need for success in this ever-evolving industry.', 'The World of Food Packaging', 4, '2024-04-19', NULL, '2024-04-18 08:06:58'),
(59, 5, 'Making Home A Comfortable Place With Soft Couches & Sofas', 'comfort-of-couches-and-sofas', 'While converting a house into a home, the first thing that comes to mind is comfort. And the most comfort that people seek is provided by the couches or sofas. These pieces of furniture aren\'t merely places to sit; they are the heart of our homes, where we unwind after a long day, gather with loved ones for laughter-filled conversations, and indulge in cozy moments with a good book or movie.', 'Let\'s embark on a delightful exploration of the world of couches and sofas, where comfort meets style, and every design choice tells a unique story.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/59_oBnkkKgO-.jpg?updatedAt=1713438388820', 2, 'Home Comfort: Finding Perfect Couch And Sofa Sanctuary', 'Discover the art of finding the perfect comfort in sofas and couches. From plush softness to firm support, make every lounging moment feel like home sweet home.', 'Home Comfort', 6, '2024-04-20', NULL, '2024-04-18 08:08:41'),
