(72, 7, 'A Guide to Garbage Removal Jobs and How to Land One', 'garbage-removal-jobs', 'Garbage removal is an essential service that ensures our communities stay clean and environmentally safe. It\'s an often-overlooked job, but garbage collectors play a vital role in waste management and public health. With a steady demand for workers, this career path can offer job security, decent pay, and the satisfaction of positively impacting society. ', 'Garbage removal could be the right fit if you\'re looking for a hands-on, physically active job that doesn\'t require years of schooling. Here\'s a breakdown of what the job involves, the skills you need, and tips on how to land one.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/72_FDiAgGcIP2.jpg?updatedAt=1728043549793', 3, 'How to Land a Garbage Removal Job: Your Essential Guide', 'Find out how to start a career in garbage removal. From skills and qualifications to job-acquiring tips, we\'ve got you covered.', 'Garbage Removal Jobs', 2, '2024-05-28', NULL, '2024-10-04 09:55:28'),
(73, 7, 'Meat Packing Jobs: The Heartbeat of the Food Industry', 'meat-packing-jobs', 'The meat packing industry is a vital part of the food production process. It is responsible for converting livestock into meat products in grocery stores and restaurants. While it may not be glamorous, meat packing is essential in ensuring that meat is processed, packaged, and ready for consumers. ', 'In this blog, we will explore the meaning of meat packing jobs, their importance, and career opportunities in this industry.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/73__-zGF8CWWl.jpg?updatedAt=1728043549784', 3, 'Why are Meat Packing Jobs the Core of the Food Industry?', 'Explore the crucial role of meat packing jobs in the food industry, their impact on safe meat processing, and the career opportunities they provide.', 'Meat Packing Jobs', 3, '2024-10-29', NULL, '2024-10-04 10:00:44'),
