(75, 7, 'Picker and Packer Jobs: A Quick Guide to Warehouse Roles', 'picker-and-packer-jobs', 'Picker and packer jobs are essential in the logistics and supply chain industry. As online shopping and e-commerce continue to grow, the demand for skilled warehouse workers, including pickers and packers, is rising. These jobs are crucial to ensuring that products are delivered to customers accurately and on time. Let’s understand what a picker and packer job entails, who is best suited for the role, and how to get hired today!', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/75_Picker%20and%20Packer%20JobsA%20Quick%20Guide%20to%20Warehouse%20Roles_oSEOgB3g2o.jpg?updatedAt=1728044536697', 2, 'Everything You Need to Know About Picker and Packer Jobs', 'Want a picker and packer job? Learn the day-to-day tasks, necessary skills, and tips on how to find and secure picker and packer positions today.', 'Picker And Packer Jobs', 5, '2024-05-31', NULL, '2024-10-04 10:10:37'),
