(87, 5, 'Senior Living Communities Guide & Money-Saving Strategies', 'senior-living-communities-money-saving-guide', 'Senior living communities are intricately designed to cater to the diverse needs of older adults, offering a wide array of services, amenities, and care choices. The extensive range of options can evoke excitement and overwhelm for seniors and their caregivers as they transition into senior living.', 'Discovering the perfect community that aligns with your lifestyle, requirements, and financial constraints necessitates a comprehensive examination and comprehension of each choice\'s features. Here, we will introduce you to various senior living communities and provide cost-effective tips to ease your transition into this new chapter of life.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/87_dvIHcoSJ1s.jpg?updatedAt=1728043549751', 3, 'Affordable Senior Living: A Comprehensive Guide', 'Discover the intricacies of choosing the perfect senior living community that suits your budget and lifestyle. Get ready for a worry-free retirement today!', 'Senior Appartments', 1, '2024-06-12', NULL, '2024-10-04 11:08:08'),
(88, 3, 'Breaking the Myth: Is Psoriasis a Microbial Infection?', 'is-psoriasis-a-microbial-infection', 'Psoriasis is a complex and often misunderstood condition. Despite affecting millions worldwide, myths surrounding its cause continue to circulate, with one common question being, \"Is psoriasis a microbial infection?\" This misconception has led to unnecessary confusion and stigma for those living with the condition.', 'In this blog, we will debunk this common myth and help you better understand psoriasis and its causes.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/88_KoGzSXRS3D.jpg?updatedAt=1728300166092', 3, 'Debunking the Myth: Is Psoriasis a Microbial Infection?', 'Is psoriasis a microbial infection? Learn the truth behind psoriasis, its causes, and why people often mistake it for an infection.', 'Is Psoriasis a Microbial Infection', 2, '2024-06-13', NULL, '2024-10-07 11:26:16'),
(89, 3, 'Asthma: 5 Symptoms You Need to Watch Out For', 'symptoms-of-asthma', 'Asthma can often feel like navigating a maze with no map. It affects millions worldwide, yet many remain unaware of its early signs. Such lack of awareness may make you feel lost and can often delay diagnosis and treatment, thereby impacting your overall quality of life. ', 'Knowing what to watch for is crucial if you or your loved ones suspect asthma. In this post, we\'ll highlight 5 key asthma symptoms and offer insights to help you identify them early.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/89_AZgIxMLVnu.jpg?updatedAt=1728300165925', 2, 'Understanding Asthma: 5 Critical Symptoms to Watch For', 'Asthma can be elusive. Learn about the 5 key symptoms that could indicate asthma and how to seek appropriate care.', 'Asthma', 3, '2024-06-14', NULL, '2024-10-07 11:31:21'),
(90, 3, 'The Itch That Won\'t Quit: Navigating Atopic Dermatitis', 'what-is-atopic-dermatitis', 'Atopic dermatitis, commonly called eczema, is more than just a skin condition; it’s a daily battle for millions. Characterized by relentless itching and inflammation, this chronic ailment often begins in childhood and can linger into adulthood, affecting self-esteem and overall quality of life. ', 'In this blog, we will explore the intricate causes and symptoms of atopic dermatitis and provide practical management strategies to help those affected regain their comfort and confidence.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/90_yM4i32x2Q.jpg?updatedAt=1728300165884', 2, 'Understanding the Itch: Insights into Atopic Dermatitis', 'Struggling with atopic dermatitis? Learn about its causes, symptoms, and proven management techniques to minimize flare-ups and improve your quality of life.', 'Atopic Dermatitis', 4, '2024-06-15', NULL, '2024-10-07 11:34:34'),
(91, 3, 'Understanding Depression Tests: A Guide to Mental Health Awareness', 'a-guide-to-depression-tests', 'Depression can often feel like a shadow that follows us everywhere, casting a dark hue on our brightest days. But how do you know when it\'s not just a bad day but something more? That\'s where depression tests come into play. These assessments help individuals identify symptoms of depression, offering a starting point for understanding their mental health.', 'In this blog post, we\'ll explore how depression tests work and why they might be a valuable tool for anyone suspecting they might be struggling with depression. Whether you\'re curious about your mental health or want to support someone else, understanding these tests can be a step toward seeking the right help.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/91_LmKVRSi60Q.jpg?updatedAt=1728300166167', 3, 'Depression Tests: A Guide to Mental Health Awareness', 'Discover how depression tests work and their role in mental health awareness. Learn about the differences between online and in-person screening tests.', 'Depression Test', 5, '2024-06-16', NULL, '2024-10-07 11:39:51'),
