(95, 3, 'Gastroenterologists: 5 Telltale Signs You Need One Today', 'when-to-visit-a-gastroenterologist', 'Have you been feeling a bit off lately? Maybe your stomach\'s been acting up, and you\'re unsure why. While occasional digestive issues can be normal, there are times when it\'s crucial to consult a specialist. ', 'In this post, we\'ll explore 5 telltale signs that it might be time to see a gastroenterologist. Whether it\'s persistent discomfort or unusual symptoms, understanding when to seek expert advice can make all the difference in your health and well-being.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/95_JLJNlztav8.jpg?updatedAt=1728300165988', 3, '5 Signs You Need to See a Gastroenterologist Now', 'Heartburn, bloating, or gas becoming too frequent? Find out how a gastroenterologist can address these issues and help improve your gut health.', 'Gastroenterologists', 1, '2024-06-20', NULL, '2024-10-07 11:54:20'),
