(152, 3, 'Understanding Tardive Dyskinesia: Signs, Treatments & More', 'understanding-tardive-dyskinesia', 'Tardive dyskinesia (TD) is a neurological disorder that occurs as a side effect of long-term use of antipsychotic medications. These medications, while essential in managing psychiatric conditions like schizophrenia or bipolar disorder, can lead to involuntary movements in various parts of the body. This condition can be distressing and significantly impact a person’s quality of life. ', 'Here, we’ll explore the signs of tardive dyskinesia, potential treatments, and how to manage the condition effectively.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/152_H8olfxw59V.jpg?updatedAt=1729508067827', 3, 'Tardive Dyskinesia: Causes, Signs and Treatments', 'Learn how to identify the symptoms of tardive dyskinesia and understand its causes, signs, and latest treatment solutions for managing symptoms.', 'Tardive Dyskinesia Signs Treatments', 1, '2024-08-15', NULL, '2024-10-21 10:00:08'),
(153, 3, 'Multiple Sclerosis Treatment Options You Must Know', 'multiple-sclerosis-treatment', 'Multiple sclerosis (MS) is a chronic autoimmune disease that affects the central nervous system, causing damage to the brain, spinal cord, and optic nerves. It is estimated that over 2.5 million people around the world are affected by MS, with women being two to three times more likely to develop the disease than men.', 'While there is currently no cure for MS, there are various treatment options available that can help manage symptoms and slow down the progression of the disease. The most common treatment approaches for MS include medication, physical therapy, lifestyle changes, and alternative therapies. Here\'s a brief explanation of each treatment option you can implement today.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/153_q_U7F3adJn.jpg?updatedAt=1729508068254', 2, 'Understanding Multiple Sclerosis Treatment Options', 'Learn about treatment options for multiple sclerosis and how medications, therapies, and lifestyle changes can help manage MS symptoms.', 'Multiple Sclerosis Treatment', 2, '2024-08-16', NULL, '2024-10-21 10:02:14'),
(154, 3, 'A Guide to Leukemia: Signs, Causes, and Treatments', 'leukemia-guide', 'Leukemia is a word that can stir a lot of emotions and questions, but understanding it is the first step towards managing its impact. This blood cancer affects millions worldwide, yet many people still find it confusing or intimidating. ', 'In this guide, we\'ll break down leukemia into simple terms, discussing what it is, its signs, causes, and available treatments. This post will provide clarity and insight into this complex disease, whether personally or supporting a loved one.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/154_mzjagyXai.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654357', 2, 'Leukemia Guide: Understanding Signs, Causes and Treatments', 'Learn everything you must know about Leukemia, including its signs, causes, and treatment options. Gain insights to manage this challenging blood cancer.', 'Leukemia Signs Causes Treatment', 3, '2024-08-17', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:10:08'),
(155, 3, 'Everything You Need to Know About Bone Density Tests', 'all-about-bone-density-tests', 'Bone density tests might not be a topic you often consider, but they are crucial in maintaining your skeletal health, especially as you age. If you\'ve ever wondered why these tests are essential, how they work, or when you should consider getting one, you\'re in the right place. We’re covering everything you need to know about bone density tests in a conversational and informative way.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/155_KRT5JD3BC.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654410', 3, 'Bone Density Tests: Everything You Need to Know', 'Bone density tests help maintain bone health, identify early signs of osteoporosis, and more. Learn how they work and who should get tested today!', 'Bone Density Test', 4, '2024-08-18', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:12:29'),
(156, 5, 'Why Choose Private Jet Rentals for Your Next Trip?', 'why-to-choose-private-jet-rentals', 'Have you ever imagined traveling in ultimate luxury, free from the hassles of commercial air travel? Consider the world of private jet rentals, where luxury meets convenience. For discerning travelers seeking comfort, flexibility, and privacy, renting a private jet offers an unmatched experience. In this post, we’ll explore why private jet rentals are becoming increasingly popular and why they might be the perfect option for your next trip.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/156_2VC2ycfF4q.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654883', 3, 'Why are Private Jet Rentals a Smart Choice?', 'Find why private jet rentals are a smart choice for travelers. The benefits are endless, from luxury and privacy to flexible schedules and cost efficiency.', 'Private Jet Rentals', 5, '2024-08-19', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:14:59'),
(157, 3, 'What is Nash? | Signs, Causes, Treatments and More', 'nash-signs-causes-treatments', 'Nonalcoholic Steatohepatitis (NASH) is a liver condition that often flies under the radar but can have serious health implications if not addressed. As a more severe form of nonalcoholic fatty liver disease (NAFLD), NASH involves the accumulation of fat in the liver, leading to inflammation and liver damage. This condition can progress to cirrhosis, liver failure, or even liver cancer. ', 'Living with NASH can be challenging, but with the right information and proactive management, it\'s possible to mitigate its effects and maintain a healthy liver. So, it\'s essential to understand what NASH is, its causes, what early symptoms to look out for, and how it can be treated.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/157_kZvGRHYR50.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654747', 2, 'All About NASH: Signs, Causes, Treatments and More', 'NASH is a severe liver condition that can lead to cirrhosis and liver cancer.  Uncover its signs, causes, and treatments to mitigate this silent condition.', 'Nash signs Cause Treatment', 6, '2024-08-20', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:17:40'),
(158, 5, 'How to Find the Right Oil Change Specials For Seniors', 'tips-to-find-oil-change-specials-for-seniors', 'Keeping your car in top condition is crucial, especially as it ages alongside you. Regular oil changes are vital for vehicle maintenance, but costs can quickly increase with time. If you\'re retired or living on a fixed income, finding ways to save on oil changes becomes even more critical. Fortunately, there are several smart strategies to keep your vehicle running smoothly without breaking the bank.', 'Here, we explore practical tips to help seniors save on oil changes. Whether snagging a discount or avoiding unnecessary costs, these strategies make maintaining your car affordable and hassle-free.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/158_s29rUPIrQS.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654874', 2, 'Tips to Find the Right Oil Change Specials for Seniors', 'Find the best ways for seniors to reduce oil change expenses with coupons and special offers. Maintain your car affordably with our smart tips.', 'Oil Change Specials For Seniors', 7, '2024-08-21', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:19:47'),
(159, 5, 'Essential Tips for Choosing the Right Retirement Village', 'how-to-choose-a-retirement-village', 'Choosing a retirement village is a significant decision that requires careful consideration and planning. It’s not just about finding a place to live; it’s about finding a community that meets your lifestyle needs, health requirements, and personal preferences. With so many options available, the process can feel overwhelming. However, with the right approach, you can find a retirement village that offers a fulfilling and comfortable living experience.', 'Retirement should be a time of relaxation, enjoyment, and new experiences. A well-chosen retirement village can provide the perfect environment for this next chapter of your life. Here are some tips to help you make an informed decision.', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/159_FffwzhYWWT.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654890', 3, 'How to Choose the Best Retirement Village', 'Get tips for selecting a retirement village that suits your lifestyle and health needs. From budgeting to location, learn how to choose the right one for you.', 'Retirement Village', 8, '2024-08-22', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:23:51'),
(160, 2, '5 Benefits of Registered Nursing Program Online', 'benefits-of-registered-nursing-program-online', 'The healthcare field is constantly evolving, and one of the most significant changes in recent years has been the rise of online education. Online registered nursing programs have become increasingly popular, offering flexibility and accessibility that traditional programs may lack. If you’re considering a career in nursing or looking to advance your current nursing education, here are 5 benefits of enrolling in a registered nursing program online.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/160_9DOML_o_D4.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654406', 3, 'Top 5 Benefits of Registered Nursing Program Online', 'Enhance your nursing career through online education. Understand how online RN programs offer accessibility and convenience for aspiring nurses.', 'Registered Nursing Program Online', 1, '2024-08-23', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:30:04'),
(161, 3, 'Parkinson’s Disease: Signs, Treatment & More', 'parkinsons-disease-signs-and-treatment', 'Most of us have heard of Parkinson’s disease, but what does it entail? This chronic and progressive neurological disorder affects movement, muscle control, and balance, and it usually creeps up gradually. Famous faces like Michael J. Fox and Muhammad Ali have brought visibility to the condition, yet many aspects of Parkinson’s remain misunderstood. Let’s break it down in a way that’s both informative and easy to understand.', '', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/syin0m2gb/fmr/161_VJEuqWImff.jpg?updatedAt=1729594654658', 2, 'Understanding Parkinson’s Disease: Signs and Treatments', 'Learn about Parkinson’s disease, its symptoms, causes, and treatment options. Get insights into managing life effectively with Parkinson’s.', 'Parkinsons Disease Signs Treatment', 2, '2024-08-24', NULL, '2024-10-22 10:32:01'),
